{"tid":299411,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Ben Affleck《暗算》拍續集","createTime":"2017-06-27T05:30:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-27T11:30:56.000Z","uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"77a9a8e348aa3261781e050418d84e2672315190","tid":299411,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T05:30:51.000Z","msg":"去年上映，以小兵立大功之姿創下賣座佳績的「會計師」，成本僅4000萬美金(約新台幣12.8億)，卻創下全球1億5500萬美金(約新台幣49.6億)的票房，成績斐然。根據「Deadline」報導，華納兄弟影業打鐵趁熱，將確定推出續集，男主角班艾佛列克已經點頭答應回歸，導演蓋文歐康納則在洽談中，而在首集戲分吃重的喬柏恩瑟，目前可能會因為要出演Netflix戲劇「制裁者」，如果檔期未確定，可能會無法出演。"},{"pid":"031e88cb7ed25bf4b1b4fbd00199e555392fa6dc","tid":299411,"uid":29628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T05:32:58.000Z","msg":"會計佬好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e05d146277724b50ddaae16fda11fccb12d154a","tid":299411,"uid":84228,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T05:36:53.000Z","msg":"會計師：正義曙光"},{"pid":"0c6e644c1dc8f4d111588b8f96335d8b0da76358","tid":299411,"uid":49151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T05:41:22.000Z","msg":"呢套好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9edd0e83f6ebc6b2f87bd4413648776b86da404","tid":299411,"uid":99911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T05:45:20.000Z","msg":"兄弟嗰幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f8e8bcaa207f8a102df25ec7a8d2ef53175882","tid":299411,"uid":54431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T05:45:53.000Z","msg":"呢套正啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3560f250ed06bf02bb8e7f7e9945ee8e7ba3ee3","tid":299411,"uid":105567,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T06:30:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://vignette1.wikia.nocookie.net/marveldatabase/images/1/16/Punisher_and_Batman_Deadly_Knights_Vol_1_1.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20080